Class TasksListMenuBean

java.lang.Object
  oracle.apps.fnd.applcore.customization.menu.taskslist.TasksListMenuBean

public class TasksListMenuBean
extends java.lang.Object

This class provides the model for Tasks List menu items. It also provides operation methods for manuipulating the tasks list menu node.

Deprecated. 

Setter for the custClasses property. This custClasses property is used to set the customization level for the CRUD operation on this menu item. If it is not set the operation will use the tip level set in the MDSSession custConfig object.
